# --- User data (NEVER tracked publicly) ---
# All medical results, source PDFs, exports, backups, and the optional
# tunnel token live under DATA/LabResultsArchive/ on each user's own
# machine. Per CLAUDE.md non-negotiable #4, the app's data folder is
# gitignored by design.
DATA/
*.env

# --- Build artifacts (PyInstaller .exe is rebuilt locally; not versioned) ---
*.exe
build/
dist/
*.spec
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# --- Virtual environments ---
.venv/
venv/
env/

# --- Editor / OS / local tooling ---
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.code-workspace
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
